item.description: Nike Definition Racerback Sports Bra: Sweat-wicking support. Sporting a sweat-wicking combo of breathability and snug support, the Nike Definition Racerback Women's Sports Bra is a hard-working, contoured essential that flatters while taking on medium-impact workouts. Ideal for medium-impact sports like like cycling, dance and cardio classes. Fabric: 88% Polyester/12% Spandex

With a compression fit for support and a tie-dye pattern, the breathable Nike Colour Me Happy Printed Indy Women's Sports Top is a workout-ready design with style. Sweat-wicking fabric and a distraction-free seam construction tackles any low-intensity activity, while a restriction-free racerback profile ensures lasting comfort. Ideal for light-impact sports like walking, weight-training and yoga. Benefitting from Dri-FIT fabric to wick sweat away and help keep you dry and comfortable, mesh-lining for a breathable fit, racerback with mesh panel for range of motion and comfort and flat-seam construction to minimise chafing. Fabric: 61% Cotton/33% Polyester/6% Elastane

Breathable wire channelling wicks away sweat to keep you dry and double layered fabric for extra softness against the skin. Two ways to wear - fasten normally or cross-over straps. the flat wing design with no hard corners and no irritating labels.
